~~ Location | Punta Cana
~~ Category | Empirical Human Data Collection
~~ Public | If you ask who Germany's "Christian Drosten" is, a simple answer is that he's their "Anthony Fauci".  We create a system to automatically generate these adaptations, which can help improve cross-cultural understanding and create new training data for tasks like question answering.
